      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata n  5-4 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline/>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p>
                     <lb/>            Carisfima Oliva<lb/>            Finalmente! Credevo pro-<lb/>            pro che mi avessi dimenticato! Speriamo <lb/>            che, come dici, mi scriverai più sovente per <lb/>            l'avvenire. Godo nel saperti in salute;<lb/>            mi meraviglia la tua nuova profefsione<lb/>            Perchè? E i tuoi scolari? Puoi vivere sen-<lb/>            za di loro? E il latino? Non potrò a vere l'o-<lb/>            nore di chiamarti profefsorefsa? Dirai che sono <lb/>            Molto curioso, anzi più indiscreto che curioso, <lb/>            ma che vuoi mi meraviglia talmente il <lb/>            tuo nuovo indirizzo, che a rischio della <lb/>            tua collera , permetto di formularti<lb/>            queste domande. Fammi sapere qualche <lb/>            cosa, scrivimi a lungo, non cominciare <lb/>            niente però e mi farai <lb/>            veramente piacere. Io sto <lb/>            benissimo come tutti noi e come di voi non dubito</p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <s>
                     <lb/>Saluta tutti caramente anche <lb/>a nome di mamma e <signed>
                        <persName>
                           <forename ref="Nino">Nino</forename>
                        </persName>
                     </signed>e <lb/>tu ricevi un abbraccio affettuoso <lb/>da Mario. </s>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 35 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
